      ],
      "content": "In the Fiscal Year 2024 report for Union Pacific in the Transportation & Logistics sector, the Fleet fuel efficiency metrics reveal significant data across several locomotives, denoted as Locomotive A and Locomotive B, alongside summarized averages. Locomotive A showcases an Efficiency Rating of 85%, with a Fuel Consumption cost of $1.20 per liter over a Total Distance of 150,000 km. Conversely, Locomotive B exhibits a higher Efficiency Rating of 90%, with a more economical Fuel Consumption cost of $1.15 per liter while covering a Total Distance of 200,000 km.",
